      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, the valvetrain has been meticulously maintained with a recent VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement\u2014addressing the chassis's known torsional stress points. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero oxidation, while the undercarriage remains free of corrosion. Mechanically flawless, this unit exhibits precise compression across all six cylinders and has had the rod bearings replaced for total peace of mind. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning driver who values mechanical purity.",
